	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002107_0001"/><!--pb/@n='19r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><!-- HEADED NOTPAPER? <placeName>Newstead Abbey</placeName>, <lb/><placeName>Mansfield, Notts</placeName>. <lb/>-->7 Nov <hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi> 1864 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p><persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">rs</hi></hi> Goodlake</persName>
<lb/>obliges me by taking 
<lb/>up two small 
<lb/>books with 
<w>astro-<lb break="no"/>nomical</w> observations 
<lb/>worked out for 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi> Arrowsmith</persName>
<lb/>but I don't send 
<lb/>the sketches by 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002107_0002"/><!--pb/@n='19v'-->
<lb/><persName>D<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi> Meller</persName> which I 
<lb/>mentioned to <persName>Cooke</persName>
<lb/>as a lady comes 
<lb/>tomorrow who 
<lb/>may construct 
<lb/>something out of 
<lb/>them for me. </p>
<lb/><p>A small tract 
<lb/>of <persName>archbishop 
<lb/>Whately</persName> &amp; published 
<lb/>by Parker &amp; Co I 
<lb/>think teaches that 
<lb/>several things 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002107_0003"/><!--pb/@n='20r'-->
<lb/>such as iron-making 
<lb/>fire &amp;c &amp;c indicate 
<lb/>Divine revelation<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I want to shew 
<lb/>by the similarity 
<lb/>of a great many 
<lb/>things the probability 
<lb/>that this was the 
<lb/>case. Can you 
<lb/>get me the tract 
<lb/>indicated - the 
<lb/>name I have forgot<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>It is an argument 
<lb/>for a Revelation 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002107_0004"/><!--pb/@n='20v'-->
<lb/>from some things 
<lb/>that savage man 
<lb/>could not have 
<lb/>attained without 
<lb/>divine aid. If you 
<lb/>can you will 
<lb/>oblige<reg>.</reg> Yours ever </p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
